- `aitbc trade list` — List active trades
- `aitbc trade chains` — List chains available for trading
- `aitbc trade get <trade_id>` — Get trade details
- `aitbc trade status <trade_id>` — Get trade status
- Implementation: Create `cli/aitbc_cli/commands/trade.py` and register in `cli/aitbc_cli/core/main.py`

